<TEXT>
<P>
I am writing in response to Gerald Peary's March 4 article on the movie "The 
Handmaid's Tale." 
</P>
<P>
I was appalled by his embracing of stereotypes of fundamentalist Christians. 
</P>
<P>
Of course there are extremist and hypocrites in all religions, but what this 
