<HEADLINE>
<P>
PUBLIC HEARING SET ON VIA VALMONTE CLOSING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A public hearing will be held Wednesday at Torrance City Hall to determine the 
environmental impacts of closing Via Valmonte in Torrance at the boundary of 
Palos Verdes Estates. 
</P>
<P>
The street on the city's southern boundary is a major access road leading into 
and out of the peninsula city. 
</P>
<P>
Torrance council members instructed city planners to do the environmental study 
following complaints by residents over growing congestion along the road. The 
council's move has enraged many Palos Verdes Estates residents, who say they 
would face a major inconvenience if the street is closed. 
</P>
</TEXT>
