<HEADLINE>
<P>
MAYOR PROCLAIMS WEEK OF YOUNG CHILD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
WHITTIER 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mayor Victor Lopez has proclaimed Monday through April 9 the Week of the Young 
Child. Lopez issued the proclamation last Wednesday. Kathleen Pompey and Norma 
Stryker, co-chairs of the Week of the Young Child Committee for the Whittier 
Chapter of the Southern California Assn. for the Education of Young Children, 
accepted the mayor's proclamation. 
</P>
