<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA040190-0107 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 197944 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 1, 1990, Sunday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 1; Column 2; Sports Desk 
</P>
