<HEADLINE>
<P>
WESTLAKE'S EBY TO ATTEND UCLA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Westlake High's Mike Eby gave an oral commitment to UCLA on Friday after 
limiting Channel Islands to one hit in the Warriors' 1-0 Marmonte League 
victory. 
</P>
<P>
Eby, a 6-foot-2, 190-pound senior left-hander, has a career record of 16-7 at 
Westlake and holds five school records. Eby is 4-0 this season with an 
earned-run average of 0.77. He narrowed his choices to Cal State Northridge and 
UCLA. 
</P>
</TEXT>
