<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAME IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The St. Louis Cardinals put relief pitcher Todd Worrell, who is coming off 
elbow surgery, on the 60-day disabled list. 
</P>
</TEXT>
