<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
HUBBLE SPACE TELESCOPE; DISCOVERY (SPACE SHUTTLE); SPACE PROGRAMS -- UNITED 
STATES; SPACE EXPLORATION; ASTRONOMY; TELESCOPES 
</P>
