Los Angeles Times; Photo, The heat is on in Tustin Relay prelims: Andre 
Ashcraft (left) and Scott Johnson of Huntington Beach pass the baton, 
Saddleback's Eddie Salinas is first in 800 relay and . . . 
</P>
