<P>
Photo, COLOR, The hottest Jackson today is featured in MTV's "Janet Jackson 
Rockumentary" airing April 21, the same week the singer will be playing to 
sell-out crowds at the Forum in Inglewood. AL SEIB 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
